and conversion to a package. Instead of using GPG for token storage, this package uses Keyring.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS mutt\-oauth2
.sp
Obtain and print a valid OAuth2 access token.
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
